Package org.planit.input

Class InputBuilderListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.planit.input.InputBuilderListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, EventListener, org.djutils.event.EventListenerInterface
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PlanItInputBuilder, TntpInputBuilder
    public abstract class InputBuilderListener
extends Object
implements org.djutils.event.EventListenerInterface
    Listener which is automatically registered to the creation of any traffic assignment component for which it gets notified. @see #TrafficicAssignmentComponentFactory.TRAFFICCOMPONENT_CREATE
    Author:
    markr
